    </div>

    <div class="candidate-leftColumn">
        <div class="mbox bool-application-activities">
            <div class="mbox-title">Activities</div>
            <div class="candidate-activities"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="candidate-rightColumn">
        <div class="mbox bool-application-comments">
            <div class="mbox-title">
                Comments <a class="applicationAskForCommentButton btn btn-mini pull-right">New Ask For Comment</a>
            </div>
            <div class="candidate-comments"></div>
            <form class="form-horizontal reply-for-comment-form" hidden>
                <input type="hidden" name="commentID">
                <div style="text-align: center;padding: 1em;">
                    <div class="control-group" style="text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0">

                        <div class="user-note-avatar"></div>
                        <p class="bool-application-comments-note" readonly class="ask-4-comment-note"></p>

                    </div>
                    <div class="control-group" style="text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0">

                        <div class="commenter-note-avatar"></div>
                        <textarea flexible
                                  class="bool-application-comments-comment"
                                  name="comment" placeholder="leave your comment here...">
                        </textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <a class="bool-edit-comment-btn btn btn-mini btn-info pull-right"
                                >Edit</a>
                        <a class="bool-cancel-comment-btn btn btn-mini btn-danger pull-right" hidden
                                >Cancel</a>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-mini btn-success pull-right">
                            Reply
                        </button>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="bool-alert-group">
                    <div class="alert alert-dismissable alert-info bool-alert-toast hide">
                        <a class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">&times;</a>
                        <strong>Sending </strong> ask for comment...
                    </div>
                    <div class="alert alert-dismissable alert-danger bool-alert-toast hide">
                        <a class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</a>
                        <strong>Faield </strong> to send ask for commnet. Retrying in
                        <span class="bool-retry-timeout">10</span>s...
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info"
                                data-loading-text="Sending ...">
                            Try now
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="alert alert-dismissable alert-success bool-alert-toast hide">
                        <a class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">&times;</a>
                        Ask for comment has been sent
                        <strong>successfully.</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mbox" style="height: auto">
        <div class="mbox-title">Workflow</div>
        <div class="candidate-workflow">
            <div class="candidate-workflow-stages">

                <div class="candidate-workflow-stage pending">
                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="1">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Pending</strong> stage. You can:</div>
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Make an interview</a>
                        <a class="offerButton">Offer a job</a>
                        <br/>
                        Don't know what to do?
                        <a class="askForCommentButton">Ask for comment</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="candidate-workflow-stage interviewing">

                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="1">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Interviewing</strong> stage.</div>
                        You planned an interview on <span class="interviewDate">Date-Time</span>.
                        We're waiting for applicant's response. Although you can:
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Reschedule an interview</a>
                        <a class="offerButton">Offer a job</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="2">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Interviewing</strong> stage.</div>
                        Applicant can't come on <span class="interviewDate">Date-Time</span>. You can:
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Reschedule an interview</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="3">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Interviewing</strong> stage.</div>
                        Interview will be hold on <span class="interviewDate">Date-Time</span>.
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Reschedule an interview</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="4">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Interviewing</strong> stage.</div>
                        Interview is hold on <span class="interviewDate">Date-Time</span>.
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Make an other interview</a>
                        <a class="offerButton">Offer a job</a>
                        <br/>
                        Don't know what to do?
                        <a class="askForCommentButton">Ask for comment</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="candidate-workflow-stage offered">
                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="1">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Offered</strong> stage.</div>
                        We're waiting for applicant's response.
                        Although you can:
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Make an other interview</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="2">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Offered</strong> stage.</div>
                        This is applicant response: <span>Accepted</span>
                        You can:
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it and notify somebody about this response</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="3">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Offered</strong> stage.</div>
                        This is applicant response: <span>Declined</span>
                        You can:
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it</a>
                        <a class="archiveButton">Archive it and notify somebody about this response</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="candidate-workflow-stage archived">
                    <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="1">
                        <div>Application is in <strong>Archived</strong> stage. You can:</div>
                        <a class="interviewButton">Make an interview</a>
                        <a class="offerButton">Offer a job</a>
                        <br/>
                        Don't know what to do?
                        <a class="askForCommentButton">Ask for comment</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="candidate-actions">
    </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

